DESCRIPTION:Taught by Jo Anne Iaciofano. Grab your mat\, kick off your shoe
	s\, and join this Pilates-inspired class to improve body movement\, core s
	trength\, and muscle control. This beginner’s friendly class\, using mind-
	body connection and breath\, will take you through a series of exercises w
	ith an emphasis on technique and fluidity. We will focus on those areas mo
	st stressed during gardening by using your core to power the muscles incre
	asing your energy and endurance. All levels are welcome. Wear comfortable 
	clothing and be prepared to workout barefoot. Please bring a yoga or Pilat
	es mat\, towel\, and water. This class will take place in the Aaron Educat
	ion Center.  $17.50 BBGS Member/$25 Non-Member.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcit
	y.com/events/#/details/pilates-for-gardeners/17923217/2026-03-27T00\n\nFro
